```

### Command Context Methods (for slash commands)

```typescript
// Wait for idle
await ctx.waitForIdle();

// New session
await ctx.newSession({ withSession: (ctx) => { /* setup */ } });

// Fork session
await ctx.fork(entryId, { withSession: (ctx) => { /* setup */ } });

// Navigate tree
